<emphasis id="266B1F6FBD04C42B9C9B03FF8D859925" bold="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
(paratypes). BRAZIL. 
<normalizedToken id="35E91047A017D05D3833B2C82E6940D4" originalValue="Paraná">Parana</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
: Campo Largo, Caverna do Pinheirinho, fl., fr., 13 Oct 1996, G. Tiepolo &amp; A.C. Svolenski 716 (EFC, MBM). 
<emphasis id="EF60AB362FA4CC9421ADCE8AB439D790" bold="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Rio de Janeiro</emphasis>
: Itatiaia, Serra do Itatiaia, Maromba, fl., 23 Oct 1931, C. Porto 2101 (RB). 
<emphasis id="AE307BE8B7DDE874EDEB9675B9C0F866" bold="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Santa Catarina</emphasis>
: Rio do Sul, estrada Rio do Sul-Lontras, fl., 3 Dec 2013, A.L. Gasper et al. 3270 (FURB). Rodeio, borda da floresta, fl., fr., 10 Oct 2015, L.A. Funez 4549 (FURB). Urubici, Salto do rio Avencal, fl., fr., 16 Oct 2004, G. Hatschbach et al. 78097 (MBM). 
<normalizedToken id="3B893AE2DAD3617298CF68304CA460EB" originalValue="São">Sao</normalizedToken>
Miguel 
<normalizedToken id="A5C9500EE2BCA6F73578AE0D911DC568" originalValue="D’Oeste">D'Oeste</normalizedToken>
, forest above rio 
<normalizedToken id="99DBEAD5747EE6EA5CB4A229A6907910" originalValue="Reperi-guaçu">Reperi-guacu</normalizedToken>
