<normalizedToken id="FC076B146427A8513454D7C06114B9CA" originalValue="Leitão-Filho">Leitao-Filho</normalizedToken>
&amp; G.J. Shepherd 2536 (MBM, NY, UEC); loc. cit., ca. 10 km SW de 
<normalizedToken id="B76F3CE48D6E98507B645A2D57286D03" originalValue="Jundiaí">Jundiai</normalizedToken>
, fl., fr., 8 Oct 1976, H.F. 
<normalizedToken id="8A3A1A636F00F67B926BA09C20E68FCE" originalValue="Leitão-Filho">Leitao-Filho</normalizedToken>
et al. 3175 (E, MBM, NY, UEC, UFG, US). 
<normalizedToken id="5895631152B6530C63275091282792E6" originalValue="Salesópolis">Salesopolis</normalizedToken>
, 
